metadata.description:
We launched 999 Stellar Senses avatars into space, each one equipped with its own unique combination of traits that will help guide us on our mission.

Every Stellar Senses NFT comes with a Full-Length Song, including some killer remixes! Your Stellar Spaceman might be vibing out to some Vapor Wave or chilling to a House edit.

“Stellar Senses” is the initial step in Nota's mission to support creators and collectors in the digital age.

Holders of this NFT will own the commercial rights to the visual graphics and avatar, and receive a worldwide and unlimited streaming license to the music.

In the future, Nota will release music NFT's with song ownership and royalties for token holders, so make sure you pick up our first-generation NFTs to get access to our mega drops in the pipeline!

Songs include: “Senses” by KINGDØMS (Original) (Pop), BrillLion Remix (Future Bass), Claurish Remix (Synthwave), Maxi Rozh Remix (Future House), BuenoChino Remix (Electro Pop), JDL Remix (House), FlyFox Remix (Future Dance)
